(40, 12, 17, 42, 21, 22, 22, NULL, 'Fulfillment of Prophecy', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of fulfillment, with Matthew referencing a prophecy by Esaias and Luke indicating that all things written will be fulfilled. This connection highlights the continuity of prophetic fulfillment in the biblical narrative.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
